org.ensembl.variation.driver
Interface IndividualAdaptor

All Superinterfaces:
Adaptor, java.rmi.Remote
public interface IndividualAdaptor
extends Adaptor

This adaptor provides database connectivity for Individual objects. Individuals may be retrieved from the ensembl variation database by several means using this module.

Author:
Craig Melsopp

fetch

public java.util.List fetch(Individual parent)
                     throws AdaptorException
Retrieves all individuals which are children of a provided parent individual. This function operates under the assumptions that Male individuals can only be fathers, Female individuals can only be mothers and Unknown individuals can only be one or the other - not both.

Returns:
zero or more children of the specified parent.
Throws:
AdaptorException
